Writing games with Ruby

RubyConf 2010
Mike Moore
November 13, 2010

The first example game demonstrates moving objects on the screen.

  ruby demo_game.rb

The second example creates an animated sprite that you can control.

  ruby sprite_game.rb

The third example demonstrated clipping and simple game mechanics.

  ruby patrol_game.rb

The last example is a mostly working game where you avoid ev1l snakes
so you can attend RubyConf.

  ruby rubyconf_game.rb
